In the second column of Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 2007/2000, the following amendments shall be incorporated:
1. for order Nos 09.1571 and 09.1573:
— CN code ‘ex 0305 59 90’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘ex 0305 59 80’;
— CN code ‘ex 0305 69 90’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘ex 0305 69 80’;
2. for order Nos 09.1575 and 09.1577:
— CN code ‘ex 0304 20 95’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘ex 0304 20 94’;
— CN code ‘ex 0305 59 90’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘ex 0305 59 80’;
— CN code ‘ex 0305 69 90’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘ex 0305 69 80’;
3. for order No 09.1515:
— CN code ‘2204 21 83’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘2204 21 84’;
— CN code ‘ex 2204 21 84’ shall be replaced by CN code ‘ex 2204 21 85’.
